high_descs: Move towards the white door, then turn left and move towards the refrigerator, then turn left and move to the range then turn right and move to the sink in front of the window.
Pick up the knife with the gold handle in front of the black cup from the sink.
Turn right, move towards the refrigerator, then turn right and move to the end of the counter next to the two yellow chairs.
Slice the tomato closest to the end of the counter using the knife.
Turn to the right and move to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the knife on the right bottom shelf in front of the white plate and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn around and move to the end of the counter then turn right and face the counter.
Pick up the tomato slice nearest to the end of the counter.
Turn right and move to the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator doors, place the tomato slice on the top left shelf to the right of the mug, chill the tomato slice, open the refrigerator, pick up the tomato slice from the shelf, and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn left, move towards the black microwave then turn right and face the gray coffee maker.
Place the tomato slice on the counter in front of the coffee maker and to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Walk towards the door, turn left towards the stove, and turn right towards the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife from the sink.
Turn around and head towards the counter.
Slice the tomato on the left edge of the counter into several pieces.
Turn around and head towards the fridge.
Open the fridge and set the knife in front of the plate.
Turn around and head towards the sliced tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Turn around and head towards the fridge.
Place the tomato next to the cup in the fridge, close it to let it cool, and then take it back out.
Turn left towards the coffee maker on your right.
Place the tomato slice in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool, sliced tomato in front of the coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk straight then turn left, then right towards the sink
Take the knife from the sink
Walk with the knife towards the counter
Slice the tomato on the counter
Walk with the knife towards the fridge
Put the knife inside the fridge
Walk towards the counter
Take a slice of tomato
Walk with the slice of tomato towards the fridge
Put the slice of tomato inside the fridge, close it and open it again to take the slice
Walk towards the sink, turn left
Put the slice of tomato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Grab a knife, cut a slice of tomato, put it on the fridge put it on the counter
